        <!-- How RAG AI Works -->
        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-orbitron font-bold text-primary mb-6">How RAG AI document retrieval Works / Implementation</h2>
          
          <div class="mb-8">
            <p class="text-lg text-white leading-relaxed mb-6">
              RAG AI implementation involves sophisticated technical architecture combining vector databases, embedding models, and large language models. The system creates a semantic understanding of your document corpus, enabling intelligent retrieval and contextual response generation.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-orbitron font-bold text-white mb-6">Technical Architecture Components</h3>
            
            <!-- Image: Technical architecture - Left positioned, medium size -->
            <div class="float-left mr-10 mb-8 w-56" style="float: left; margin-left: 1rem; margin-right: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; margin-top: 1rem; width: 14rem; max-width: 14rem; clear: left;">
